OL,3,CLifeshare homeless charity please for
OL,4,Chelp to meet "unprecedented" demand
OL,6,FGranada Reports' journalist, Tim
OL,7,FScott, has been along to the shelter
OL,8,Fin Manchester.
OL,10,FManchester's oldest homeless charity
OL,11,Fsays it needs public support "now more
OL,12,Fthan ever" as it marks its 40th
OL,13,Fanniversary.
OL,15,FLifeshare has supported thousands of
OL,16,Fpeople down the years - but with
OL,17,Fservices currently "significantly
OL,18,Fstretched" and fewer grants available,
OL,19,Fthere are fears over its future.
