OL,3,CLifeshare homeless charity please for
OL,4,Chelp to meet "unprecedented" demand
OL,6,FThe executive officer, Julie Vickers,
OL,7,Fis appealing for people to "dig deep
OL,8,Fand support" the work they do.
OL,10,FShe added: "Today, Lifeshare still
OL,11,Fcontinues to offer the growing
OL,12,Fhomeless community and others in food
OL,13,Fand fuel poverty the very first point
OL,14,Fof contact they might have with
OL,15,Faccessing any support services.
OL,17,F"Our Breakfast Project - every Friday,
OL,18,FSaturday and Sunday morning - offers
OL,19,Fpeople a hot meal, showers, clothing
OL,20,Fand conversation.
OL,26,@rD@LOU
