OL,6,F"We never judge or push someone, just
OL,7,Fsignpost them or spend time
OL,8,Facknowledging them. Our guests are the
OL,9,Fmost marginalised in the community -
OL,10,Fignored by most.
OL,12,F"Only a year ago, we were probably
OL,13,Fserving 150 people a weekend, jump to
OL,14,Four 40th year and right now we're
OL,15,Fserving upwards of 400 a weekend."
