OL,3,CLifeshare homeless charity please for
OL,4,Chelp to meet "unprecedented" demand
OL,6,FJudy continued; "Our service is needed
OL,7,Fmore than ever. Our amazing team of
OL,8,Fvolunteers come week in week out to
OL,9,Fserve our guests, but the costs are
OL,10,Frising on a daily basis. We need your
OL,11,Fsupport now more than ever.
OL,13,F"That's why our anniversary is
OL,14,Fbittersweet - we wish we weren't
OL,15,Fneeded."
OL,17,FLifeshare was founded in 1984 by David
OL,18,FGrey, who, alongside a small cohort of
OL,19,Fvolunteers, recognised an issue with
OL,20,Fpeople sleeping rough in Manchester
OL,21,Fcity centre.
