OL,4,Chelp to meet "unprecedented" demand
OL,6,FOver the years, Lifeshare has
OL,7,Fpioneered some of the most
OL,8,Frecognisable services for the homeless
OL,9,Fcommunity in Manchester including
OL,10,Flaunching a Harm Reduction Service,
OL,11,FRent Bond Scheme, bringing the Big
OL,12,FIssue to the North West and a
OL,13,FResettlement Service with Manchester
OL,14,FCity Council.
OL,16,FMatthew Johnson, Chair of the Board of
OL,17,FTrustees at Lifeshare, said:
