OL,3,CLifeshare homeless charity please for
OL,4,Chelp to meet "unprecedented" demand
OL,6,F"Last year we served over 15,000
OL,7,Fmeals. So far this year, we've served
OL,8,F11,280 breakfasts to the homeless
OL,9,Fcommunity.
OL,11,FThese are unprecedented figures for
OL,12,Fus, and now, we're asking for your
OL,13,Fsupport once more - especially as
OL,14,Fwinter is around the corner and is our
OL,15,Fbusiest time. Cash, clothing,
OL,16,Fvolunteers, personal essentials - we
OL,17,Fare asking for your help.
