OL,6,FWithout funds and our incredible
OL,7,Fvolunteers, our charity won't exist,
OL,8,Fhelp us help others and work towards a
OL,9,Ftime when maybe our charity won't be
OL,10,Fneeded."
OL,12,FLifeshare is celebrating its
OL,13,Fanniversary with a special fundraiser
OL,14,Fon Wednesday 9 October at the Lowry
OL,15,FHotel in Salford.
